MOOD_PROMPTS["calm"]="What sensory input helped or hurt today?|What did I do today just for me?|What helped me transition between tasks?|When did I feel most like myself today?|What am I grateful for right now?|Was there a moment of flow? What triggered it?|What did I learn by doing instead of thinking?|What felt effortless today?"

