MOOD_PROMPTS["frustrated"]="What executive function challenge showed up?|What decision drained me today?|What boundary did I wish I had set?|What did I need but did not ask for?|What am I avoiding right now?|What pulled my focus away today?|What did I postpone that I actually had energy for?|What would I change about how today went?"

# reflective (low-mid+/pos): prompts about processing, patterns, meaning, self
MOOD_PROMPTS["reflective"]="What helped me transition between tasks?|When did I feel most like myself today?|What small win went unnoticed today?|What did I do today just for me?|What did I learn by doing instead of thinking?|What sensory input helped or hurt today?|Was there a moment of flow? What triggered it?|What pattern do I see repeating lately?"

